---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Breadcrumb from "../../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
import CTA from "../../components/CTA.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Website Pakketten - Tarieven"
  description="Professionele website vanaf â‚¬29 per maand. Geen grote investering vooraf, wel direct online gevonden worden in de Bollenstreek."
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[
    { label: "Home", href: "/" },
    { label: "Tarieven", href: "/tarieven/" },
    { label: "Websites" },
  ]} />

  <!-- Hero with loss-aversion hook -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-5xl"
        >
          Een professionele website.<br />
          <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Geen grote investering.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Elke dag dat klanten je niet online vinden, lopen ze naar je concurrent.
          Wij bouwen je website, zorgen dat je gevonden wordt, en houden alles up-to-date &mdash;
          <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">vanaf &euro;29 per maand.</strong>
        </p>
        <a
          href="/diensten/websites/"
          class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-primary-600 transition-colors hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300"
        >
          Meer over wat we doen
          <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust bar -->
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Geen lange contracten
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Binnen 2 weken online
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Lokaal &amp; persoonlijk
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing cards -->
  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
      <!-- Anchor text -->
      <p class="mb-10 text-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Alle pakketten inclusief hosting, SSL-certificaat en technisch onderhoud. Prijzen excl. BTW.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Tier 1: Online Basis -->
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            Online Basis
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Voor ondernemers die snel online willen zijn
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">&euro;29</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">/maand</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-medium">
            Geen opstartkosten
          </p>

          <ul class="mt-8 flex-1 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Professionele one-page website
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Mobielvriendelijk design
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Click-to-call &amp; e-mailknop
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Google Maps-vermelding
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              SSL &amp; hosting inbegrepen
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Maandelijks onderhoud &amp; updates
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="mt-8 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-primary-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600 transition-colors hover:bg-primary-50 dark:border-primary-400 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:bg-primary-900/20"
          >
            Start vandaag
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 2: Professioneel (highlighted) -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary-600 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg dark:border-primary-400 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 rounded-full bg-primary-600 px-3 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white dark:bg-primary-400 dark:text-gray-900">
            Meest gekozen
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            Professioneel
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Voor bedrijven die willen groeien via hun website
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">&euro;59</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">/maand</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            + &euro;249 eenmalig opstartkosten
          </p>

          <ul class="mt-8 flex-1 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Alles van Online Basis, plus:</strong>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Contactformulier met notificaties
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Meerdere pagina&rsquo;s (tot 5 pagina&rsquo;s)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              SEO-optimalisatie voor lokale vindbaarheid
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Google Analytics &amp; zoekresultaten
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Maandelijks prestatierapport
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Koppeling met Google Mijn Bedrijf
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Snelle content-aanpassingen inbegrepen
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="mt-8 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-primary-700"
          >
            Kies Professioneel
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 3: Groei -->
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            Groei
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Voor ambitieuze ondernemers die online willen domineren
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">&euro;99</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">/maand</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            + &euro;499 eenmalig opstartkosten
          </p>

          <ul class="mt-8 flex-1 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Alles van Professioneel, plus:</strong>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Onbeperkt pagina&rsquo;s
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Blog of nieuwssectie
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Geavanceerde SEO-strategie
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Online reserveringen of afspraken
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Social media-integratie
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              Persoonlijk kwartaalgesprek
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="mt-8 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-primary-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600 transition-colors hover:bg-primary-50 dark:border-primary-400 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:bg-primary-900/20"
          >
            Kies Groei
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Monthly framing comparison -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
          Minder dan een kop koffie per dag. Goedkoper dan &eacute;&eacute;n gemiste klant per maand.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Add-ons -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 py-20 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Extra mogelijkheden
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        Breid je pakket uit wanneer je er klaar voor bent. Alles op je eigen tempo.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Webshop</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Online verkopen met betalingen en voorraadbeheer.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Vanaf +&euro;49/maand</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Google Ads</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Adverteren in Google voor directe zichtbaarheid.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Vanaf +&euro;29/maand</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Social media</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Content en beheer van je social media kanalen.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Vanaf +&euro;39/maand</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">AI Chatbot</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">24/7 klantenservice op je website met AI.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Vanaf +&euro;39/maand</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Social proof / why us -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Waarom ondernemers in de Bollenstreek voor ons kiezen
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Lokaal &amp; persoonlijk</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            We zitten om de hoek. Geen anoniem callcenter, maar een gesprek aan de keukentafel. We kennen de regio en de markt.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Snel online</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Geen maanden wachten. Met slimme technologie staat je website binnen twee weken live. En hij is snel &mdash; echt snel.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Eerlijke prijs</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Geen verborgen kosten, geen dure verrassingen. Je weet precies wat je betaalt, elke maand. Opzegbaar na 12 maanden.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Free scan CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white py-16 dark:border-gray-700 dark:from-primary-900/20 dark:to-gray-900">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Benieuwd hoe jouw website scoort?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        Doe de gratis website-scan en ontvang binnen 24 uur een persoonlijk rapport met verbeterpunten.
        Geen verplichtingen, wel direct inzicht.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/ai-scan/"
        class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-accent-600 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
